com.annimon.stream

Class Optional<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.annimon.stream.Optional<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the inner value

    public class Optional<T>
extends Object
    A container object which may or may not contain a non-null value.
